In [5]:
def Distribution(columne,data):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(1,2, figsize = (15,5))
    font_dict = {'fontsize': 14}
    title=['Kdeplot','Boxplot']
    ax = np.ravel(ax)
    
    sns.set(style='whitegrid')
    sns.kdeplot(data=data,x=columne ,ax = ax[0],color='r').set_title(title[0])
    sns.boxplot(data=data,x=columne ,ax = ax[1],palette='magma').set_title(title[1])

    ax = np.reshape(ax, (1, 2))
    plt.tight_layout()
